#: C/drapes.xml:17(title)
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Introduzione"

#: C/drapes.xml:18(para)
msgid ""
"Desktop Drapes is a wallpaper manager application for the Gnome desktop. You "
"can change your wallpaper by clicking the Desktop Drapes icon on the "
"toolbar, and set it to switch wallpaper every time you boot and at a "
"predefined interval. Also, you can tell Desktop Drapes to monitor a "
"particular directory to add wallpapers automatically."
msgstr ""

#: C/drapes.xml:21(title)
msgid "Using Desktop Drapes"
msgstr "Usare Desktop Drapes"

#: C/drapes.xml:24(screeninfo)
msgid "The display tab"
msgstr "La scheda display"

#: C/drapes.xml:30(para)
msgid "The Display tab of the Preferences window"
msgstr ""

#: C/drapes.xml:35(para)
msgid "To switch wallpapers:"
msgstr "Per cambiare sfondo:"

#: C/drapes.xml:38(para)
msgid ""
"Left-click the Desktop Drapes icon in the toolbar to switch to a randomly "
"selected wallpaper, OR..."
msgstr ""

#: C/drapes.xml:41(para)
msgid ""
"Right-click the Desktop Drapes icon in the toolbar and double-click the "
"thumbnail image of a wallpaper to switch to that wallpaper."
msgstr ""

#: C/drapes.xml:44(para)
msgid "To add a wallpaper to Desktop Drapes collection:"
msgstr "Per aggiungere uno sfondo alla collezione:"

#: C/drapes.xml:47(para) C/drapes.xml:56(para)
msgid "Right-click the icon in the toolbar and select 'Preferences'."
msgstr ""

#: C/drapes.xml:50(para)
msgid ""
"In the 'Display' tab, click the 'Add' button and select your wallpaper file "
"or files. Desktop Drapes will automatically categorize your wallpaper by the "
"dimensions of the image (I guess)."
msgstr ""

#: C/drapes.xml:53(para)
msgid "To remove a wallpaper from the Desktop Drapes collection;"
msgstr "Per rimuovere uno sfondo dalla collezione:"

#: C/drapes.xml:59(para)
msgid ""
"In the 'Display' tab, select the wallpaper you wish to remove and click the "
"'Remove' button."
msgstr ""

#: C/drapes.xml:64(title)
msgid "Customizing Desktop Drapes"
msgstr "Personalizzare desktop Drapes"

#: C/drapes.xml:67(screeninfo)
msgid "The general tab"
msgstr "La scheda generale"

#: C/drapes.xml:73(para)
msgid "The General tab of the Preferences window"
msgstr ""

#: C/drapes.xml:80(para)
msgid ""
"Start Desktop Drapes on start: Select this option to load Desktop Drapes "
"automatically when you start up your computer."
msgstr ""

#: C/drapes.xml:83(para)
msgid ""
"Switch wallpaper on start: Select this option to switch to a different "
"wallpaper every time you start Desktop Drapes. Select this and the first "
"checkbox to switch to a different wallpaper every time you start your "
"computer."
msgstr ""

#: C/drapes.xml:86(para)
msgid ""
"Timing selection: Use this slider bar to tell Desktop Drapes how often to "
"switch to a new wallpaper, from a minimum of five minutes to a maximum of "
"two hours. Move the slider all the way to the right to tell Desktop Drapes "
"never to switch wallpapers while it's running."
msgstr ""

#: C/drapes.xml:89(para)
msgid ""
"Wallpaper search directory: Select the checkbox to have Desktop Drapes "
"monitor a directory and automatically add files in that directory to its "
"collection. Click the directory list box in order to select which directory "
"Desktop Drapes should monitor. Warning: In the current version of Desktop "
"Drapes, saving a file directly into that directory will cause Desktop Drapes "
"to crash and lose its collection! Instead, save a file to a different "
"directory, then copy it into your monitored directory."
msgstr ""

